snippet.textDisplay:
Yes I'm weak, and weaks are prone to commit mistakes. Although i want to reach to You (God) and my love (ishq e haqiqi) for you is so profound and deep, i still feel so weak and powerless. Its my desire to reach to you, to see you, but i am being poisoned by the lust and pleasures of this world which subsequently has made me more weak. 

The strong waves and tidings of rivers ( the trials of this world) is making me weak, while I'm on an unbacked clay pot ( kacha garha/ my body) floating in middle of river (world)

My soul (sohni/ my reality) eagerly wants to meet You. But  Im not sure would this clay pot would be able to make me reach to you or would make me sink in this water. 

https://youtu.be/TrPvQvbp3Cg
